tutory offence黎架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c48d3888617a59afc24578ea364a78d5f43fc0","tid":1100400,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T11:41:11.000Z","msg":"諗起有BBC條紀錄片講彭定康廢除一條鎮壓性法例, 如果當年彭定康無做到, 林鄭家陣肯定日日拎黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6cfZ_xR8ZAg?t=126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6cfZ_xR8ZAg%3Ft%3D126&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBToICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=01311b64\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6cfZ_xR8ZAg?t=126</a>"},{"pid":"2be7f8339e785fcd81c89e81e998aa9fa4e1d142","tid":1100400,"uid":78143,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T11:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SGGir3o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSGGir3o.gif&h=2451a142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jMnNkop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjMnNkop.jpg&h=b225bd22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccb4fa99d4910457b08a98f718f9495f68dbdab7","tid":1100400,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T11:43:06.000Z","msg":"頭先港台先講法律<br />\n法律點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c25ffc2fc16f0bfa6eb6bc3159d3776f656c55","tid":1100400,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"英國夠膽未取消佢居英權囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a7dbd7406ad40c23f3466e121df460cd47dbaf","tid":1100400,"uid":5489,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T11:57:34.000Z","msg":"Common law 既精神就係case by case 咁不停review 睇下舊既裁決係咪適用<br />\n每個High Court既法官都權力唔跟從甚至推翻過時既法律<br />\n<br />\n有呢條法律存在唔代表你可以任意apply落今日既情況<br />\n正如謀殺曾經定義為&lsquo;unlawfully killing... with malice (惡意) aforethought&rsquo;： Sir Edward Coke (1797)<br />\n之後都因為太唔清晰 百鳩幾年後 定義為要有意圖殺人/ 意圖造成嚴重人體傷害 先叫做謀殺：R v Cunningham (1982) House of Lords<br />\n<br />\n呢種言論完全係否定左成套common law system 既價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然 作為一個傻閪/ 問另一個傻閪攞legal advice 既傻閪<br />\n呢種講法當然fit哂觀感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「關我撚事呀 係個官判佢有罪」<br />\n分分鐘仲要係鄭若嬅教佢咁講添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781c1942a0dc6f9b5747a137d2eb70a6025a4bf4","tid":1100400,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47a7dbd7406ad40c23f3466e121df460cd47dbaf","tid":1100400,"uid":5489,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T11:57:34.000Z","msg":"Common law 既精神就係case by case 咁不停review 睇下舊既裁決係咪適用<br />\n每個High Court既法官都權力唔跟從甚至推翻過時既法律<br />\n<br />\n有呢條法律存在唔代表你可以任意apply落今日既情況<br />\n正如謀殺曾經定義為&lsquo;unlawfully killing... with malice (惡意) aforethought&rsquo;： Sir Edward Coke (1797)<br />\n之後都因為太唔清晰 百鳩幾年後 定義為要有意圖殺人/ 意圖造成嚴重人體傷害 先叫做謀殺：R v Cunningham (1982) House of Lords<br />\n<br />\n呢種言論完全係否定左成套common law system 既價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然 作為一個傻閪/ 問另一個傻閪攞legal advice 既傻閪<br />\n呢種講法當然fit哂觀感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「關我撚事呀 係個官判佢有罪」<br />\n分分鐘仲要係鄭若嬅教佢咁講添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T12:53:08.000Z","msg":"唔講咁遠<br />\n用佢個logic，nazi依法治國都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05b1572d54943fae91027f067e7251d39baea89","tid":1100400,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T13:55:00.000Z","msg":"佢痴咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor